snippet.title: Atari 8-bit:- Moonbase IO
snippet.description:
shooting and maneuvering thru a debris field is only part of the mission, fight off enemies and protect your cities on the moonbase.
I do not remember exactly when I added this diskette to my collection, many decades ago, didn't seem familiar replaying it now.
